Class MarkerSymbol

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
      • edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.symbol.Symbol
        • edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.symbol.MarkerSymbol
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PictureMarkerSymbol, SimpleMarkerSymbol

    public class MarkerSymbol
extends Symbol
    Marker symbols are used to draw points and multipoints on the graphics layer. MarkerSymbol has no constructor. Use SimpleMarkerSymbol or PictureMarkerSymbol.
    Author:
    Justin Merz
